Name: assign_worker_to_team
DataType: 1 if worker w is assigned to team t

Name: assign_team_to_project
DataType: 1 if team t is assigned to project p

Name: assign_user_story_to_sprint
DataType: 1 if user story u is assigned to sprint s

Name: assign_task_to_worker
DataType: 1 if task tsk is assigned to worker w

Name: select_feature_for_release
DataType: 1 if feature f is selected for release rep

Name: assign_role_to_worker
DataType: 1 if role r is assigned to worker w

Name: set_user_story_priority
Description: Integer variable for the priority of a user story us.

Name: set_sprint_start_date
Description: Date variable for the start date of a sprint sp.

Name: set_task_effort
Description: Continuous variable for the effort of a task tsk in hours.
